### Registar um novo utilizador
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "teste5",
  "email": "test5@gmail.com",
  "password": "minhaSenhaSegura"
}

### Obter token de autenticação
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test5@gmail.com",
  "password": "minhaSenhaSegura"
}

### Obter User
GET http://localhost:8080/api/me
content-type: application/json
Authorization: bearer {{tokenteste1}}

### Apagar User
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/4
content-type: application/json

### Listar todos os users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
content-type: application/json

### Criar um lobby
POST http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenteste1}}

{
  "name": "Lobby teste",
  "description": "Descrição do lobby",
  "minPlayers": 2,
  "maxPlayers": 3,
  "rounds": 2,
  "ante": 50
}

### Listar todos os lobbies
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies

### Obter lobby por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/25


### Juntar-se a um lobby
POST http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/4/join
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenteste3}}


### Sair de um lobby
POST http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/3/leave
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenteste1}}

### Listar jogadores de um lobby
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/25/players

### Obter host do lobby
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/4/host

### Obter players de uma partida
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/2/players

### Listar todas as partidas
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches

### Obter detalhes de uma partida
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/2

### 7) Abrir ligação SSE (mantém stream)
GET {{base}}/api/matches/sse/3/events
Accept: text/event-stream

### 8) Enviar um comando para a partida (gera evento)
POST {{base}}/api/matches/sse/3/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenteste1}}

{
  "action": "roll"
}

